name: Ext_R5_QuestionnaireResponse_identifier
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.QuestionnaireResponse.identifier for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents QuestionnaireResponse.identifier from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/QuestionnaireResponse|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

element.short: Business identifier for this set of answers
element.definition: Business identifiers assigned to this questionnaire response by the performer and/or other systems.  These identifiers remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.
element.comment: `QuestionnaireResponse.identifier` maps to R4 `QuestionnaireResponse.identifier`. So is mapped as Equivalent.
